pageContext.claim: “As soon as Democrats sent their best Election stealing lawyer, Marc Elias, to Broward County they miraculously started finding Democrat votes. Don't worry, Florida - I am sending much better lawyers to expose the FRAUD!”
pageContext.analysis: Broward County was the center of the 2000 presidential election scandal. What the president is describing is more counting than "finding." It takes time to count all the votes including absentee ballots. There's no evidence of voter fraud.
